###
# Endpoint para eliminar configuración de torneo
# DELETE /api/v1/tournaments/{tournamentId}/configuration

### Eliminar configuración del torneo con ID 1
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

### Eliminar configuración del torneo con ID 2
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/2/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

### Verificar que la configuración fue eliminada (debería retornar error 404 o configuración vacía)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Flujo completo: Crear -> Verificar -> Eliminar -> Verificar eliminación

### 1. Crear configuración de torneo
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "numberOfGroups": 2,
  "teamsPerGroup": 4,
  "teamAssignments": [
    {
      "teamId": 1,
      "groupName": "A"
    },
    {
      "teamId": 2,
      "groupName": "A"
    },
    {
      "teamId": 3,
      "groupName": "B"
    },
    {
      "teamId": 4,
      "groupName": "B"
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Verificar que se creó correctamente
GET http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Eliminar la configuración
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Verificar que se eliminó correctamente
GET http://localhost:7071/api/v1/tournaments/1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json
